comments: ["Misleading. It's one of those annoying apps that you have to answer questions, then it sets up a course and then wants you to pay. No sign of the dog whistle feature in the name. Got as far as the cost screen and uninstalled it.", "Not so much judgement on the app just totally not what I wanted & the purpose wasn't filled. I wanted a whistle for our dog. & Even did not work. LOL There are different frequencies that maybe I don't know enough about, but she never responded to those either. This app is more about training exercises & offers heaps more help if you pay with a few free tips. She's already done training though, she was being cheeky, smart & testing us back. That's what we wanted the whistle for. Thank though.", "Takes forever to load. Signed up for the year bc it was cheaper than paying monthly. Absolutely do not care for how it's set up. You can not register multiple puppies, and most of the content is locked unless you sign up for premium. Why should you have to sign up for premium when you already have to pay to use the app. It should all be included. Also, I wish the videos had text to read as well as the video. I like to read then watch the videos if I'm stumped. Waste of money for me seeing as I h", "I paid for a year, thinking it would be a years with if content... nope. There wasn't 2 months of training and, finishing that doesn't open up more content to explore, learn and teach. I wish I could ask for a refund, total waste of money.", 'Pretty good! Nice, clean UI and bite-sized training segments. Pricing for the yearly sub is very fair IMO (comes out to about $2/month). I do wish that there were text transcripts of each lesson below the video though.', 'I choose not to enroll in 7-day free trial. I dont feel comfortable entering my information on an app, that i havent even got to try yet. SUGGESTION: Give people 7 or 14 day free trial, before asking for subscription yearly $39.99 I think. I want to try out an app, before commiting to purchases. Since I cannot try app, I will look elsewhere. Losing a potential customer, right away. Because dont offer free trial, before requiring payment info. Sad üò¢', "This app was very fun to use the one problem I have is you can only learn like one or two things and you have to pay for it when I could learn from a book and have that book forever and only have to pay once and it's by the month so yeah I wish there was more free courses my dog and I are trying to do a fun little routine and I thought this app would be way more useful than it was", 'I have subscribed to annual plan. My credit card has been charged but the purchase is not reflecting on my account. If I try to restore purchase it says "Billing Problem". Developer either sort out the issue or refund my subscription amount INR2150. Thanks....', "First the negative. I tried to signup on the monthly. But they took payment for the full year. So very disappointed. Can't see anyway of getting in contact with them about it. Hav8ng said that the content does seem quite well put together. But don't think it will keep us interested for the full year. So I feel like I have wasted some of my money", "Very good content especially if your interested in Canine psychology, it really takes the guesswork out of trying to decipher how best to motivate dogs and really get them invested, even looking forward to train together in a way that's fun and engaging helping create a stronger bond between you and your dog in the process.", 'Really awful app, keeps closing when I look a certain lessons, waste of time and money., I subscribed to your app and it still crashed. On several occasions, how do I get a refund.', 'Amazing app, it is just awesome how they combine teaching, games, classes, videos, information. It is all in one app, I highly recommended to all levels , from begginers to experts.', "THIS IS NOT A DOG WHISTLE APP. I downloaded this, thinking it would be a dog whistle app, maybe with other tips and tricks. I won't be paying ten bucks a month for a whistle app. Cool concept, but false advertising. Deleted.", "This app delivers all the information I need to bring up my puppy, in bight-sized, easy to consume chunks. The video tutorials are well delivered and there's also written material to reinforce and complete your learning. This, along with the daily notifications, is helping me stay focused on bringing Griswald up to be a good, good boy.", "Love this app, very I formative and useful. The only thing I would change is the order of the puppy training. It would have been nice to have some of the foundation skills first but I didn't know. Numbering them or something to that effect would make it even better.", 'I\'ve just started using this app for a couple of weeks, and I must admit that I\'m fully enjoying it! It\'s supper helpful ‚ò∫Ô∏è in my journey to adopt a new puppy (today is the day!) üê∂ So i\'m a newbie with dogs and frankly this app is the source of truth and my personal "magic wand". Thanks, guys for making it and catch huge kudos from me üëè!', 'Great app for dog training. I used the "Zen Game" to teach my dog self control and the leave it command. She caught on quickly. It also has lots of tricks and games for dogs. I can\'t wait to try them with my Pittie!', 'I love the videos to show exactly how to do it. I have trained my dogs before on my own but usually on a few things and stuff we just figure out while growing. But I love this app and all the training help. My new puppy and I are starting out, I have plans to make him the best dog ever.', 'Once i activated the free trial and tried it, i immediately cancelled my subscription since i dont feel that this app will be useful for me. Surprisingly it still charged my card after the free trial! I tried to have it refunded with google but ig got declined. I want to get my refund!!', 'Whistle function crashed my phone...I thought it was a fluke and strange coincidence, so I turned my phone back and one tried again and my phone crashed again the second I touched the whistle.', "This has been a great app for showing my children how to help with the training of our puppy. It's so clear and we'll explained, they can watch the videos and then put it into practice. If only training the children was this easy!", "Not even loading. Just a picture of a dog. Going to uninstall and try again. Redone it and turns out you have to pay for a dog whistle app. The free trial is 3 days. They didn't even ask what breed of dog I had or even what the problem was. They just made it up as they go", 'I adopted a rescue puppy about 4 months ago. I find myself continuously coming back to this app to learn the proper way to train my dog or stop unwanted behaviors. This app has been wonderful to learn the sometimes overlooked signals our dogs do to communicate with us.', 'This app is the one which you need for your puppy the most it is wonderful you need to download it and you should see everything which is included in the trainingsp are included and what to shop and we can get shopping options here to this app is wonderful I have no words to say about it moreü§©üëçüèªüëçüèªüëçüèª I first thought give this app 4 stars because the app has the purchase in almost allthe task . But then also this app is wonderful. My request is that is remove purchase from some more tasks', 'This app is very informative and provides the information and training in a fun yet challanging way that really grips the attention of the user. Im just now starting to use it daily but i love it so far. If i run across any issues ill be sure to let you know.', 'Hey! I paid for a year subscription with trainer support. However, unable to get in touch with anyone. Would like some assistance to connect to a trainer or any person I can talk to.', "Please do not buy this app. The said a trial period of 3 days. On the 3rd day when I wanted to cancel they charged me. Not trust worthy. Plus there is nothing in the app that can't be found on YouTube Please all think twice before you buy. They will not honour their commitment", "As a first-time dog owner, I was very concerned about training my pup. Thanks to this app, I have learned a lot and the entire puppy training process doesn't seem so intimidating and difficult now. Great app üëè", "Misleading. It says the app is free but it's only 1 lesson to stop biting that is free. There is a monthly fee of $9.99 for any additional lessons.", 'I signed up and paid for a month of training and selected all training categories that would help my pup. Once I get into the app I have basically no access to any of the training selections I made unless I pay to upgrade to premium.', "I was hesitant when I saw that the app was subscription based but honestly it has so much good information and tips. Its been such a breeze to use and it's helped with my puppy and my three year old dog.", "I keep trying to push the button to buy the one year subscription with the free trainer help but it's not letting me make the purchase. I need serious help with potty training my puppy or we will have to take him back to the breederüòî.", 'This app has been great assisting me with instilling the correct behaviors from the start with my puppy. Would highly recommend from the start of your journey with your pet.', "I have waited and try canceling it's awful! I have had it over a year and nothing! Worse app to have and nothing comes from your subscription! And I'm still trying to cancel!", 'Off to a great start with my 9 week old American Bulldog. Clear and concise instructions on how to build a healthy loving relationship with your dog as well as proper ways to interact and awesome training techniques . My girl Evie already sits, comes when she is called and loves the shoo shoo game! The daily excersizes has brought new life to my Cenior dog Carlos as well! We are so impressed with this app!', 'Amazing! I have a Labrador cross Kelpie and she is a bundle of energy. This App has taught us so much as dog towners and has allowed us to give her the best experience she can have as a puppy. Recommend this App for first time dog owners for sure', "A bit too expensive, I can't justify paying that much without getting to use the app first but it still seems a bit expensive for my comfort zone but I'd have love to try it out.", 'All content is secured behind a pay wall. If you plan on sampling without inputting a payment method dont even bother.', "Not expecting to pay a subscription. Seems like it has good tips tho. But didn't pursue after asking for payment.", 'fun and easy. takes the guess work out of training and is far more affordable than a professional trainer!']

title: Dog Hotel Premium
description: Open your own dog hotel now! Look after all the doggies placed in your care. Granny Edith's poodle needs to lose some weight, beefy Lucky wants to join the fire department and little Lizzy wants to learn her first tricks. Make sure all the dogs have a nice time in your hotel and that they return to their owners happy! The features at a glance ‚òÖ Run and expand your very own dog boarding kennel! ‚òÖ Care for cute beagles, loyal labradors, agile Australian Shepherds and lots more breeds! ‚òÖ Feed and groom your doggy guests and train them in clicker training and on the challenging obstacle course! ‚òÖ Complete exciting missions. Each dog has its own story and presents you with challenging tasks! ‚òÖ Expand your boarding kennel and decorate it to your tastes with pirate baskets or a magical shower! ‚òÖ Pet and play with your dogs, or watch them frolic around together on the lawn! Care for up to eight different dogs As a fresh, young boarding kennel manager, you take control of your very own dog hotel. You'll find tasks waiting for you there. You ensure that all of the dogs are happy and satisfied during their stay. Up to eight dogs can stay in your boarding kennel at a time ‚Äì so you've got your paws full! Make sure they've got enough food, wash and brush their coats and clean their cages. With lots of good care and plenty of activities, they'll feel right at home! And of course don't forget to give them lots of loving care and attention. Play with the dogs on the lawn Happy dogs need variety and lots of fun! So it's important to give your guests enough space to run around in. You can play Frisbee or ball with them on the playing field or watch the dogs frolicking around together. Teach the dogs new tricks With DogHotel it's now also possible to train your dogs! Use the clicker, and with a bit of patience you can teach them neat new tricks and commands to perform. Labrador Lucky's owner will be thrilled when he gives him his paw when he comes to picks him up! You can improve the fitness of your furry friends on the obstacle course. Guide your dogs over obstacles, through tunnels and across wobbly tree trunks. Decorate your dog hotel! As the manager of the boarding kennel, it's also your job to make sure the place is looking neaty. The more dogs you care for successfully, the more decorative items you'll unlock. From the pirate ship bathtub to the fun sausage feeding bowl, there's something for everyone. Use them to decorate and expand your boarding kennel entirely to your own tastes. Let your imagination run wild! Support If you have questions or problems related to the app or in-app purchases, please feel free to contact us via our facebook page facebook.com/tivolamobile
summary: Open your own dog hotel and care for cute terriers, bulldogs and labradors

comments: ['The game is cute but has no other merits. It is not fun. Gaining levels opens new decoration options but no new gameplay; it just requires more repetition of the same gameplay. Since tasks are already repetitive and tedious, this means that advancing in the game makes the game less fun. As mentioned, the garden is quite glitchy. I was able to make it work, but it is still frustrating. I had playpass, so I did not pay for this game. Do not spend your money on this game.', "As many other have stated, garden doesn't function. Dog glitches trying to walk out and then you can't click the dog to play. Can't get past level 2 because I'm unable to complete the task. Also, on the obstacle course, the dog isn't lined up properly with the obstacles. So, even performing the tricks, the dog isn't going through the tunnel, over the ramp, or jumping over the bar.", "Honestly.. it's a cute game a concept. But there's some controls that are really difficult to do and understand. Like the training. Dog wouldn't even make it through the whole thing without just doing whatever it wanted. And it never ACTUALLY did the course. Oh well I guess. Not worth the money for it, that's for sure.", "Garden doesn't work. I gave tired everything I even have left the game to come back in. Have no issues with the rest of the game. I click the garden then fallow the dog outside. Click on the dog everywhere while it's outside and nothing pops up to play with it. I have even sent the other dogs out and nothing. If it worked I would give it 5 stars because it's a great little game. If it doesn't get fixed it will go to one star.", "Pretty fun game, but a couple of issues. One, I can't play with the dogs while they're in the garden (no toys), so the only way to gain care is to pet, which takes forever. Two, the obstacle course is so glitchy. Pet won't turn and gestures don't register sometimes. Other than those issues, it's an enjoyable time killer.", "Obstacle course needs some serious work. The camera should stay behind the dog at all times instead of moving around and the dog should run on it's own. It's not picking up all of the gestures. It makes the game unplayable.", "Meh. Dog obstacle course doesn't work right. After 3 dogs some of them just take way too long so early in the game to get trained. Also keeps telling me I have no internet connection which I do I'm fully connected. Pretty annoying. There's a few things that make this game not great", "I thought you used to be able to go out to garden & clicker train dogs as well instead of just in kennel..? I swore you could do take em out to train, but now it doesn't or it's just not workingü§î Also, wish you'd start adding more breeds + more kennel space ! But I do like this game, great time killer. üêæ", "The playing in the garden is really glitchy. I tell it to go in the garden then tap on it to play and nothing happens, either im doing something wrong or its just not working, i also can't call the dog back in i also cant figure out how to pet the dog either. An extra button to play with the dogs outside and even little info buttons to refresh how to do things would be useful. Sort the outdoor play thing out and i will edit my review to 5* happily", 'DogHotel is hours of fun and so addicting! I cant stop playing! There are many breeds. That gives the game variety. There are many free upgrades and levels. Its a wonderful game!', "The controls are extremely imprecise and the game doesn't exactly give you an in depth tutorial. Uninstalled.", "Obstacle course is nearly unplayable due to the dog not responding to over half of my gestures. Not sure how to play with the toys for the dogs, and training is pixel perfect gestures or otherwise the dog won't respond.", "Fun game. Lots of options, premium is totally worth it. Also I haven't had any of the problems posted about, maybe your phone/tablet is glitchy?", 'Pretty unresponsive, despite multiple attempts to reload and try again. Kinda disappointed in a game that looked really cute :/', 'Cannot play with dogs in the kennel or in the garden. Very frustrating because the only way I can improve their affection is repeatedly pet them.', "Commands don't work on obstacle course, can't pet the dogs, can't play with them. Moronic because those are things it wants you to do and you can't.", 'Great Game. Just Sometimes there is giltchy. Where the dogs disapper. we love to be able to take that dog on a walk. More Stuff to do. Thanks.', 'The entire game is glitched. Looks like it could be cute, but absolutely unplayable.', "So far I think it's a pretty good game I mean a lil blocky the dogs could look better... maybe more design's TBH you should make a dog simulator or anything really...", 'The game is really good but it only gives the chance of taking care of two dogs but there are so many rooms try to give a chance to take care of more than two dogs.', 'Needs some bugs fixed, also different training options cause it gets boring.', 'I like it but it is very buggy. It makes it difficult and sometimes even impossible to play.', 'The game was good at first then it said I had to bathe them but u cant bathe them for baths. worst game ever!!! Dont waste any time pls just find an better animal game.', 'Obstacle course is WAY too buggy. Makes the game unplayable.', "For whatever reason, I cannot send my dog to any of the areas. I can't make it past the first few minutes of the game.", "This game is fun but I'm having a hard time when they get in the garden for play time", 'Love this game! So addictive! Plus, I love dogs let alone animals! Great game!', 'I dont know how yo train. It do not give enough explanation. Im disappointed. If someone could help me thatd be great .', "Same as others have said, game doesn't work properly.", 'Text is way to small on galaxy s20.', "Not good, doesn't work, just sad", "I can't play with my dog until I upgrade my lobby and I can't do that until I make my dog happy please help me", 'this one is the same as the free except different breeds and that it i got a refund on it', 'I love this game it is so addicting and cute', 'Okay, but gets really boring after awhile.', 'Not worth the money or time', 'Awful, just terrible game.', 'Freezes up often', 'I love the game', 'Knowledge985@$Verify addressVerify address']

title: My Cat - Virtual pet simulator
description:
Have you been dreaming of getting a pet? Your dreams are coming true with My Cat. Get a kitty with the cutest pet simulator ever.

Meet your new virtual fluffy friend in simulation games. Just look into these honest cats eyes. They are melting your heart already, right? Now you can listen to its happy pleasant purr-purr engine all day long. Play with your little kitten, give it the most delicious yummies, take it for a walk and have fun every day. Our cat game is made for joy. Love your cat and it will love you back üòª

The only virtual cat that looks like and feels like a real cat. Oh, those charming cat manners. Kitten games will make you laugh every day and will become your best friend. You can even say ‚ÄúThis is my talking pet‚Äù. It is so amazing to play with a tamagotchi cat. Take your kitty wherever you want, it is always by your side. You‚Äôll always have fun with your fluffy friend.

Your purring digital pet needs your love and attention. Discover the My Cat‚Äôs adventure world.

MY CAT GAME FEATURES

üéÆ AUGMENTED REALITY. Use your smartphone camera and your virtual cat will appear right in your house or wherever you want. Cat games for girls and boys can do it now. You will love it.
üì∏ FUNNY MEMORIES. Take cute photos of your talking cat to share with friends and show off on social media.
üéÅ EXTRA ITEMS. Take care of a cat, play with it, and enjoy extra items as a reward.
üíì SO REAL. Cats react to your every touch. Stroke it or scratch its cute little nose with your finger. It is so easy to turn on your kitty‚Äôs purring engine.
üêà MORE FUN. While your virtual pet is asleep or occupied with some important cat business you can set new records in an exciting animal Match 3 games or mini games. Challenge yourself and set your own records.

Show everyone how adorable your kitten is with our pet simulator. –°atch cat adventure, how cat talk, play, and all the moments spent together with your tamagochi friend. Take amusing and memorable selfies with your AR cat and collect them in the photo gallery. But don't let your cute little virtual cat wait for too long. Cat games  made for fun. Everyone loves playing My Cat. Kid games for girls and boys are teaching them how to take care of a real baby cat. They can learn a lot through playing.

üëëPREMIUM ACCESS IN GAMESüëë
Subscribe for Premium and get unlimited access to all the game features:

‚≠êÔ∏è Unlock all premium items
‚≠êÔ∏è Unlock AR mode
‚≠êÔ∏è Free daily coins and diamonds

It is your time to get a talking cat and make your dream come true. Give it all your love and you will have the most faithful fluffy tamagotchi friend ever. Enjoy playing with My Cat virtual kitty. üíü
summary: AR tamagotchi with kitten! Take care & raise kitty cat and play mini games

comments: ["this game is adorable but allow me to save you the heartache. it's gonna cost you $10 a week to keep playing this game. just downloaded it and start the game. it'll tell you right before you start playing that it's a 3 day free trial. now I'm not sure how to make sure I don't get charged. do I just uninstall or will it still charge me if I uninstall but don't cancel somehow? I didn't sign up and I don't want charged?", "Very shady. Vip subscription popup first, infested with packs every time you exit the part of a screen. In addition, you have to pay for an item to be only used once??? I'll go play my talking Tom/Angela instead. Edit: What i mean by buying one-use items is by in-game currency, not real money.", 'I just saw this game, read the reviews and decided to check if everything is so bad. I would say that the game is quite acceptable, quite good, the children will like it. Of course there are a lot of ads and as another dude said, paid content that is easy to connect which is not very good when children play it and ruin their parents themselves without realizing it. Like Tamagotchi, standard, quite cute and just not a bad game.', 'what the heck!? it\'s not even letting you play. after downloading, took me to subscription page. you should give the people the option to be "VIP member" or just regular players. thought it was free to play, but no! it\'s like this app is forcing you to PAY PER WEEK to play!', "My child accidentally installed this game from an advertisement and bought a weekly subscription for an exorbitant amount. Fortunately I could quickly cancel the subscription and change the purchase settings on my child's device. It is clear that these greedy apps are just taking advantage of young children and rubbish purchase default settings. I'm disgusted with the unscrupulous nature of these companies.", "So many ads even after paying for no ads. I got this game for my 4 year old and he kept having trouble with ads so I payed for them to be removed, but still he kept being presented with ads and being taken our of the game. Your platforms are scummy and you're just trying to trick kids into downloading as many of your bad games by roping them in with you ads. DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS FOR YOU CHILDREN.", "My 2yr old daughter accidentally purchase this app. please help, is there a way I can be refunded for this? I tried on Google play but somehow it was declined. 500php is really a big amount for just a game she doesn't want to play either. please help", "so cute! I am going to play this game everyday, every hour I get! The basic idea is that you get to take care of a virtual kitty pet that is so cute! I mean, I can't even take it!", 'So chock full of ads. No joke, every 25 seconds there is an ad to watch and wade through. Do NOT leave your kids unattended with this game. It repeatedly prompts to subscribe to something in-game, for OVER $20 PER WEEK. The developers should be ashamed of themselves.', "super slow and glitchy. it could have just been the phone though. other than that it's a cute gameüòä", "Nice game, it took me forever to choose ONE of the three cats offered at the start of the game! They are all so adorable I wished there was a button that would let me take them all. Too bad there's a subscription tied to this game. Also the cat's noises are too human and there is one screeching noise it often does which makes me worried if it's choking or dying. The sound just doesn't make sense.", 'Might as well make us buy the game since we cant play without paying 10 dollars a month. You trick people into downloading your game thinking it was free to play but its not.', "Within the first seconds my son got an ad of a subscription he needed to pay for 17.99‚Ç¨. A WEEKLY SUBSCRIPTION. He accidentally bought it because he can't read yet and tried to close it while i forgot to put him back in kids mode. I thankfully got a refund. no where here this is mentioned. Absolutely disgusting.", 'Horrible. I paid for no ads and I still get ads, fix this! I hate having my toddler dealing with invasive ads and she still gets them! I just wanted my money', 'I was surprised when I saw payments of ‚Ç¨10.99 coming out of my account without my authorization on a monthly basis. My 6 year old daughter innocently started playing this game not realizing that there is a subscription charge. How can Google let this happen. Ban apps like these!!!', 'I like the way that the cat reacts to everything you do for him or her. I will play it alot! So thanks you so much for making this game! Biggest smiles and claps!!!', "Just wanna share how my 3 year old daughter were able to subscribe to te VIP of this app so easily. It's frustrating that google doesn't even do refunds.!!!", 'Really good, my 7 year old loves this game and the instructions are straight forward and easy to follow.', "Currently stuck on screen this is congratulations wow someone's outgrown their old things!? Was a 1% bar underneath it that has been stuck at 1% for like 3 days I'm probably going to uninstall and reinstall to see if that fixes it", "Don't download. Starts with glitchy sounds that crackle my phone speakers and goes in and out, then first thing that pops up is an huge 'ad' telling me to agree to pay a huge amount of money to just play the game!! I didn't even get to experience anything first. Automatically 0 stars. Since I backed out when the game froze while telling me to pay to play, I don't have any opinions on anything else. Didn't waste my time further, I suggest you don't either.", 'Immediately hit with paywall that was not able to be skipped... 19.99/week is ridiculous. There are better games for less. Do better.', 'I LOVE THE GAME!!!!!When i find this game i go on play store and install it.Is a veryyyy fun game.Also for persons ho want a cat but they are not shure,this game is perfect for them.You can also see what a cat do 24h.Is good for kids because they learn how to take care of a cat.', "Terrible It claims free with in app purchases but the first thing that pops up says 14.99/week and you can't get out of it!", "Couldn't get past the screen that says you have to pay 14.99 a week to play the game. Thats an outrageous price for a game.", "Can't even play it without paying ¬£8 per week. Absolute rip off and a complete waste of time.", "My daughter downloaded this app and suddenly I had a charge for ¬£8,49 for a weekly VIP subscription on my card. I just can't imagine how easy this app allows these sort of transactions, she's 5 years old and clearly pressed keys withouth knowing that she was accepting an in app purchase. I still wonder how that happened as it was allowed without password, verifications or submitting security info such as cvv for the card. I cancelled and unsubscribed straight away and Google play refuses refund", 'How do you even skip the VIP subscription screen.
